---
title: Mixed Mushroom, Beyond Meat® and Pea Cottage Pie with Cheesy Mashed Potatoes
description: This veggie take on a classic casserole combines a saucy mushroom filling with extra cheesy mashed potatoes. A quick broil at the end of cooking gives this cottage pie an irresistible golden crust.
